General.Name: Innovex International, Inc
General.Description: Innovex International, Inc. designs, manufactures, sells, and rents mission critical engineered products to the oil and natural gas industry worldwide. The company sells and rents its products to international and national oil companies, independent exploration and production companies, and multinational service companies. Its products have applications in the onshore and offshore oil and natural gas wells, including well construction, well completion, and well production and intervention. The company was founded in 2016 and is headquartered in Humble, Texas.
